name: Frank's First Ultimate Super Mario Bros. 1
overview: Frank’s first “ultimate” Super Mario Bros. hack. It’s pretty good, really, but absolutely pales in comparison to the third one. Still, if you liked that one, and are looking for more of the same, this is a pretty good bet. It has 28 levels instead of 20, essentially meaning the levels are stretched out thinner. Which means, overall, they’re not quite as interesting.
